<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }
        .booking-details { background: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin: 8px 0; }
        .detail-label { font-weight: bold; }
        .total { font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #28a745; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>ðŸŽ‰ Booking Confirmed!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{customerName}},</h2>
            <p>Great news! Your booking has been confirmed. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="booking-details">
                <h3>Booking Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Booking Number:</span>
                    <span>{{bookingNumber}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Product:</span>
                    <span>{{productName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Rental Period:</span>
                    <span>{{startDate}} to {{endDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row total">
                    <span class="detail-label">Total Amount:</span>
                    <span>{{currency}} {{totalAmount}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>We'll prepare your item for pickup/delivery</li>
                <li>You'll receive updates on the status of your booking</li>
                <li>Make sure to be available during the scheduled time</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing us for your rental needs!</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Rental Management Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Rental Management. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>